"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130750/extras/a24dc5343a0945b7846d1bb2edd5faa0.avif?t=1698309103\" width=640 height=140 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEFEAT THE BOSS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Save your friends by defeating the boss in every campaign's last map, and unlock them as a playable character.<br></li><li>It's your choice who you think is worthy of being saved first.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130750/extras/764403c78db2651802648e1ba7c51667.avif?t=1698309103\" width=640 height=101 /></span><br><br>",
